            "ignore": false,
            "order": 4,
            "anno_id": 1,
            "text": " **Theorem 1.** Let  $P \\subset \\mathbb{R}^n$  be an n-polytope. Assume  $F_P \\geq 0$ . Then P is an n-simplex.",
            "line_with_spans": [
                {
                    "category_type": "text_span",
