            "anno_id": 1,
            "text": " (here  $F_P \\geq 0$  means  $F_P(A, B) \\geq 0$  for all  $(A, B) \\in (\\mathcal{K}^n)^2$ , where  $\\mathcal{K}^n$  denotes the set of all convex bodies in  $\\mathbb{R}^n$ ).",
